### blind_watermark

The `blind_watermark` directory contains a modified version of the `blind_watermark` project (https://github.com/guofei9987/blind_watermark).

Original Copyright:
Copyright (c) 2019 郭飞

Modifications made by LuminCrypt:
- Added multi-scale embedding and extraction.
- Added adaptive RS_NSYM and block redundancy based on quality levels.
- Added edge-margin exclusion logic.
- Enhanced synchronization template with multiple peaks and rings.
- Added self-check verification post-embedding.
- Removed unused modules and simplified the CLI bridge (`bwm_helper.py`).

